title: mondaysRmurder EP 7: The Disappearance of Kelsie Schelling and her Unborn Baby
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: How could it NOT be the boyfriend! I can't believe they don't have enough to arrest him. Thanks Mary I look forward to hearing the bell telling me I have a new email on Monday morning, I know it's you with another one of these baffling cases.
Chilling as ever. Not knowing is probably the most hardest and interesting things about cases.
UPDATE: On December 1st, 2017, Donthe Lucas was arrested for the murder of Kelsie Schelling. Her body hasn't been located and there is a $50,000 reward for information.

description: What happened to Kelsie Schelling on the night of February 4th, 2013? Due to the timeline and abundance of information, mRm excluded the theory this week. To me, it's obvious what happened to this young woman, and I'm keeping hope alive for Kelsie and her family.
